    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's been happening for a few days now though... i also noticed i'm been going to the bathroom way more often than usual. i read online that drinking way more water helps with lithium. do you think if i just drink a ton of water and try to sleep it off i'll be fine? i'm really trying to avoid the clinic if i can",
